Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:05.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬豬一個人去地學奧林匹克了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:09.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  這週星期天好像會進行預選
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:14.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真令人吃驚  那孩子竟然會接受這樣的挑戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:18.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的呢  我也想去參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:21.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,四年一次太難得了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.58,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1289.371,906.571)}礦苗攀岩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地學奧林匹克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:26.79,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636.572,491.714)}化石開掘競賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,都有些什麼競賽項目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.80,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1242.971,817.514)}望遠鏡\N尋星競賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,競賽…不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:32.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:35.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因為叫奧林匹克我還以為一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在意的話就先去調查下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.44,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&HFF&\fs70\move(939.2,408.6,939.2,1131.8)}日本地學奧林匹克募集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:45.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地學奧林匹克是指  面向初高中生的地學知識競賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:46.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,每年都會舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:50.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,從通過了國內預選和終選的學生中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:53.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,挑選出去參加國際大賽的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:56.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,櫻學姐  知道得真詳細呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:58.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我家妹妹也會去參加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:00.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:02.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,櫻學姐原來有妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,現在讀初三
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:06.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,中學生就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:08.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說是在突破了預選和終選後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:11.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想去參加在泰國舉辦的國際大賽來著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:13.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,泰國…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1119.543,147.257)}想要的土特產清單
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1226.552,312.82)}泰式酸辣湯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1177.79,442.648)}泰式咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1046.362,535.447)}大象周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.30,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024.152,683.79)}泰拳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:17.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈米菈  太性急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但話說回來豬豬為什麼突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看了合宿時候的照片  一下子就來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.35,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,{\frz353.5\fs30\pos(749.667,237.111)}日本地學奧林匹克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.35,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,{\frz353.5\fs30\pos(769.667,267.667)}過去在鑑定試驗中使用過的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.35,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,{\frz353.5\fs30\pos(766.778,294.333)}岩石·礦物·化石標本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:28.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原來如此  是地質標本館裡的展示呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:30.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我以前覺得對我們這樣的小社團
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那完全是另一個世界的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:36.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,然而那孩子卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:40.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:45.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,櫻學姐  剛剛的表情變得超溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明是在表揚她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:51.45,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,===op===
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.39,Asteroid - title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1100,1100)\blur15\pos(586.133,917.466)}冬天的鑽石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這兒  以前一定是條河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,探險是之後的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天的我  是地學部的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱著強韌的心情  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.79,Asteroid - SongTi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1282.667,534)}日本地學奧林匹克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.79,Asteroid - SongTi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(838.667,507.333)}考試會場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好  好慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原來有這麼多人參加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,而且淨是些不認識的學校的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,鄰座的同學  今天多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你還挺有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是冴木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是豬瀨  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:16.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小豬瀨在緊張嗎  第一次參加？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:21.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  我們學校就只有我一人參加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:25.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,而且只要一想到在場的大家都是競爭對手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就有一種疏遠的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:28.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我去年一路走到了終試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,當然  也是抱著不會輸給其他人的心情參加的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但轉念一想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:46.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家都是些對地學有著莫大興趣的同類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,再說  大會的結果可以用於一些大學的入學申請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以這個為目標的人當然也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有這種制度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,報名表上寫著的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對夢露學姐暫且保密好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.78,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,388.667)}考試開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.78,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1397.334,510)}考試結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.78,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1709.333,676.667)}11:30以後\N可以交卷離開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,差不多了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,總之  愉快地去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:09.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小豬瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,現在開始下發試卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太厲害了  冴木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,竟然是備選經驗者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:24.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一定是個頭腦非常聰明  解題速度也很快的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是發現了獵物的野獸的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,集中集中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,首先是地質學科的題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地質羅盤磁針的讀法  疊覆律  指准化石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這部分問題解起來好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地質剖面圖  火山  岩漿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,氣象學科  海洋學科  環境學科…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是我不擅長學科的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,雖然也大致學習過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:05.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但果然沒有理解到原理的話感覺解不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最後是  天文學科
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是小行星的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,咦  比起想像中解起來輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,畢竟一直都和她們待在社團活動室裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,還有十分鐘結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:31.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…還有一道題怎麼都搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,做得快的人都已經離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:38.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,從A到O中選出兩段正確的描述
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:43.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,從A到O…從A到O…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,從A到O？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,AO！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:51.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,/註：藍的名字發音是AO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,結束了結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小豬瀨也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:05.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,腦子裡塞滿的知識一下全放空了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是  來參加真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,來到這裡第一次感覺到的東西有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:21.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比如自己是多麼渺小之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:27.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  覺得世界比自己想像的還要寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我還以為是在說身高的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,機會難得  一起走到車站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:34.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對了  我在回去路上有件事情想做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因為我在河流填上的地方發現好像有一條新的小道出現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就想去探探險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是什麼  好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,結果已經出了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒有  我自己算了下分很悽慘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是  學姐看上去似乎很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:08.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道了在這個地學部之外也有很多的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:09.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:11.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要看照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要看要看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:18.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,踏出了一步  變得比我們更成熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:21.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要回去了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看到了大家的樣子後打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我也得再加把勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這就是冴木同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是回程途中探險時的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,用了數碼相機卻沒有晃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這張是冴木同學拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我拍的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,電磁爐麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因為找遠藤老師借爐子被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我就從新屋老師那兒借來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就趕緊準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,文化社團的電閘是共用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什麼  黑暗火鍋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒  是聖誕節年終晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可以的話一起參加如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,承蒙好意  但是新聞部也在舉行年終晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以才這個打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:35.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,聖誕快樂  以及新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,被訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這就有點棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:42.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因為漏風很嚴重暖氣也不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對了  如果是石燒鍋的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石燒鍋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:52.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,把高溫的石頭投入進去烹飪的鄉土料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:10:00.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去找作為石頭的英安質熔結凝灰岩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:01.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去哪兒找？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,到男鹿半島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也找藍商量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.80,Asteroid - Chat4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1340,155)\fad(400,0)}跳閘紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,電磁爐和暖氣好像不能同時使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:29.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不開暖氣  作為代替給學姐們準備幾條毛毯之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,然後再把火鍋做辣  讓身體暖和起來怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.86,Asteroid - Chat4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(1341.333,147.334)\c&H5C6384&\3c&H8BCD84&}鱗片從眼睛裡掉出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.65,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：「鱗片從眼睛裡掉出來」有令人眼前一亮，恍然大悟的意思，源自聖經故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:43.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的是  我一直都在從米菈那兒獲得活力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是能有什麼作為回禮就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.51,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\frz6.364\pos(1032,722)}聖誕節\N\N\N{\c&H82B49A&}年終晚會！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:11:00.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,第一回  地學部年終聖誕派對  開始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒想到還能在活動室裡吃上火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我說  這金閃閃的究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈借給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在人造衛星上也有用到的隔熱毯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在JAXA參觀學習的時候買的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,確實買了各種各樣的東西呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,圍上這個後  感覺就像變成了人造衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是什麼感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是這個看上去很暖和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,火鍋的味道沒問題麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:40.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小米菈  這個火鍋好辣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:44.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只是用了超市裡賣的泡菜湯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:47.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:49.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,難道說是因為這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:55.90,Asteroid - Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,614)}辣椒粉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,追加辣味的辣椒粉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,難道說！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:12:00.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米  米菈說把所有食材都放進去  我就以為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,學姐  稍微等一下再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,味道挺刺激的還挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:12.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這難道就是大人的味覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  你拜託我要的屋頂頂上的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,屋頂？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想著等大家身子暖和起來了就去看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.85,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,泡菜火鍋  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好  好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說好的大人的味覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哇  視野好寬闊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因為今天很冷  所以夜空很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就是冬日鑽石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:49.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,天狼星  參宿七  還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,畢宿五  五車二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:53.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,北河三  南河三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,櫻學姐你是查閱過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:00.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只是因為石頭裡也有這些名字所以就不知不覺記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:01.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你在笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:06.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對了  在其中加入獵戶座的參宿四的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看起來就是大寫的G
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你說的Ｇ是英文字母的G嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  連接那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:20.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  原本是地質研的我居然也會仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對於合併還是覺得不滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是這樣想的話就不會做這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:31.97,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,大家過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是我們送給大家的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可以打開喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是相冊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我拿出了我的偷拍藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,然後麻煩小櫻編輯整理成相冊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,社團活動的場景還有活動時的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,居然拍了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有好多照片要是放上去了就顯得你們太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,挑選的時候真是費了好大力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  感覺特別開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:39.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:40.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,泡菜的功效也過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,鍋裡加點水做烏冬麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,到了這個年紀真是受不了寒冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真虧你們能穿那麼短的裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,暖氣  暖氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老師  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:05.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:13.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,即使過了三號  來參拜的人還是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,豬豬學姐  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:16.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說的也是  不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,兩張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這附近修建有規模龐大的治水工程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所有很想和以前的地圖對照一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是治水工程的紀念碑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,來拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,學姐  不如我們先去參拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說起來是啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:45.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,參拜完後抽籤再去茶屋吃糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我還想喝甜米酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:50.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是天然石的抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我好想抽一發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,從這裡好像看得不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:03.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,從顏色來看好像是水晶  瑪瑙  紅碧玉
